parameters:
Zerachiel: Ah! You were ignoring me,
huh?!

Ishvald: ...It's just that my voice is
quiet. Please don't mind it.
PushGab 4 世の中には色々な人がいるなぁ…

Ishvald: ...Vaar Castle is to the north.
You shouldn't get lost.
PushGab 4 話、聞こえていたんだね。ありがとっ！

Ishvald: ...I'll also help you, Unie and
the others.

Zerachiel: At first, I thought she was
quiet, but she's surprisingly
cooperative, isn't she?

Sachia: She's kind, isn't she? I'll also
thank her, thank you.

Ishvald: ...Lamia has been sighted in
the magic ore mountain.

Ishvald: It would be good to prepare for
the deadly poison...

Zerachiel: Deadly poison is troublesome,
isn't it?

Rabi: It would be safer to prepare
equipment with resistance.

Ishvald: ...In the Forest of Star
Singers, many monsters that inflict
status ailments have been sighted.

Ishvald: It would be good to prepare
countermeasures with a ring...

Zerachiel: Thank you for the helpful
information.

Claudia: Since I can't use
detoxification magic, it would be better
to prepare countermeasures.

Ishvald: ...Captain, I won't lose this
time.

Ishvald: When you calm down, let's have
another match.
Azel: Yes, as you wish, Ishvald-san.

Claudia: It feels like something is
about to happen.

Lala: Surprisingly, they might be in
love!!
Ishvald: ...Do you want to be slashed?

Lala: Ah, it's a lie, I'm sorry! Don't
draw your sword!! Don't raise it up!!

Knight: Oh, hello~! What can I do for
you?

Zerachiel: Um, I'm looking for
someone...

Zerachiel: Is there a knight named Unie-
san?

Zerachiel: Actually, I wanted to ask for
your help...

Unie: I would be happy to help, but
right now I have a lot of knight duties
piled up and my hands are full.

Zerachiel: Actually, Aries asked me to
talk to you, Unie-san...
Unie: Eh... Ahhh, from Lady Aries!?
Zerachiel: Huh? Ah, yes, that's right...

Unie: Geez! If it's an introduction from
Lady Aries, you should have said so
earlier!!

Unie: If I don't prioritize helping out,
I'll end up getting punished, you know!

Unie: Of course, I'll lend you my
strength!

Zerachiel: Really...? Thank you, Unie-
san!!
Unie: You can just call me Unie~♪

Unie: So, what kind of consultation is
it?

Unie: I see... It's the curse of the
evil god Orpheus, huh...
Unie: There's no doubt it's Seizetsu.
Unie: It's a curse from the god.

Unie: Unlike typical curses, this curse
is offered to the gods as a sacrifice,
even one's own life.

Unie: Effy-sama's weakening is likely
due to that.

Unie: Because it means that your very
life force is being drained.

Unie: Please rest assured! There is a
treatment for Seizetsu!

Unie: You'll need to gather some
materials, but if we make a curse-
breaking potion, we can cure it!
Probably!!

Unie: However, making a curse-breaking
potion is beyond my expertise. It's
difficult for me...
Zerachiel: Of course, I'll help too.
Unie: I still think it's difficult.

Unie: In that case, we'll need to rely
on a specialist in medicinal potions...

Unie: Zerachiel-sama, let's go to the
castle together.
Unie: Yes, the timing was good.

Unie: Right now, one of the Demon Lord's
daughters has returned...

Unie: That daughter is well-versed in
the production of elemental medicine,
it's an incredible skill. If we explain
the situation, she might lend us her
power.
Unie: Let's head there right away.

Azel: Unié, it's great to see you
looking well.

Unié: Captain, when you're free, let's
take a bath together again~!!

Azel: Ahaha... I'm fine with just taking
a shower.

Unié: Since I'm a girl, I should take
better care of my appearance, you know~?

Zerachiel: Azel, you're weak for Unié,
aren't you?

Lala: It looks like you have a good
relationship.

Claudia: Sachia and I were also like
that, you know.
